did you click the deb package in the downloads folder?
downle click the package.  That should open USC and from there click install.
i tried to install it by clicking on it and usind the gdebi package installaer but still its giving this error "Error: Dependency is not satisfiable: python-aptdaemon.gtk3widgets"
